<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/3972509-antonella">Antonella</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I&apos;m thinking about reading this book. What I gathered is that you can definitely read the Tony Foster Series on their own, but you&apos;d understand better<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I'm thinking about reading this book. What I gathered is that you can definitely read the Tony Foster Series on their own, but you'd understand better all the nuances if you read the Vicki Nelson Series first, where Tony Foster was a secondary character. Personally I don't plan to read 8 books of a m/f series for the sake of nuances ;-).<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
