<a href="/questions/650573-hey-is-there-actual-m-m-romance-in">Hey! Is there actual &quot;M/M romance&quot; in this? Kissing, sex, love in a prominent way? Or is it just alluded to or fade to black kind of stuff? I want to read some queer fantasy books with legit romance that is as relevant as hetero romance.. :)</a>
